name: $resourceType
desc: Returns the FHIR type name for this instance

name: $identifier
desc: Returns: Identifier for the TestScript assigned for external purposes outside the context of FHIR.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Identifier for the TestScript assigned for external purposes outside the context of FHIR.

name: $::name
desc: Returns: A free text natural language name identifying the executed TestScript.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A free text natural language name identifying the executed TestScript.

name: $status
desc: Returns: The current state of this test report.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The current state of this test report.

name: $testScript
desc: Returns: Ideally this is an absolute URL that is used to identify the version-specific TestScript that was executed, matching the `TestScript.url`.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Ideally this is an absolute URL that is used to identify the version-specific TestScript that was executed, matching the `TestScript.url`.

name: $result
desc: Returns: The overall result from the execution of the TestScript.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The overall result from the execution of the TestScript.

name: $score
desc: Returns: The final score (percentage of tests passed) resulting from the execution of the TestScript.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The final score (percentage of tests passed) resulting from the execution of the TestScript.

name: $tester
desc: Returns: Name of the tester producing this report (Organization or individual).

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Name of the tester producing this report (Organization or individual).

name: $issued
desc: Returns: When the TestScript was executed and this TestReport was generated.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: When the TestScript was executed and this TestReport was generated.

name: $participant
desc: Returns: A participant in the test execution, either the execution engine, a client, or a server.

name: $addparticipant
desc: A participant in the test execution, either the execution engine, a client, or a server.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: A participant in the test execution, either the execution engine, a client, or a server.

name: $setup
desc: Returns: The results of the series of required setup operations before the tests were executed.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The results of the series of required setup operations before the tests were executed.

name: $test
desc: Returns: A test executed from the test script.

name: $addtest
desc: A test executed from the test script.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: A test executed from the test script.

name: $teardown
desc: Returns: The results of the series of operations required to clean up after all the tests were executed (successfully or otherwise).

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The results of the series of operations required to clean up after all the tests were executed (successfully or otherwise).
